<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I’ve not yet been able to reach you to discuss your renewal quote over the phone.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I don’t want you to lose out on these key benefits:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Unlimited retroactive cover</b>&nbsp;- protects you against claims arising from work you completed before your current insurance policy began.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Worldwide Jurisdiction cover</b>&nbsp;- ensures that you're protected almost anywhere that your work may take you.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Nil excess</b>&nbsp;- guarantees no unexpected out-of-pocket expenses in the event of a claim.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Sub-Contractors&nbsp;</b>- includes cover for up to 3 business-facing sub-contractors (BFSCs), provided they hold the same levels of cover as you.</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">It would be good to discuss your requirements to make sure your renewal quote is right for your business.<b>&nbsp;Is there a good time for me to give you a call?<br></b></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can contact me on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you soon.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/refer-a-friend/"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""></a></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>